==Documentation==
This template creates a full theme page layout with hero section, tabs, wiki content, and sidebar.
Uses Semantic MediaWiki for structured data storage and display.

Themes are aesthetic or narrative categories - e.g., Sci-Fi, Horror, Fantasy, Post-Apocalyptic.

===Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description
|-
|| Name || Display name of the theme
|-
|| Guid || Giant Bomb API identifier
|-
|| Aliases || Alternative names (comma-separated)
|-
|| Image || Theme image filename
|-
|| Deck || Short description shown in hero
|}

===Usage===
<pre>
{{Theme
| Name = Sci-Fi
| Guid = 3032-18
| Deck = Games set in futuristic or science fiction settings...
}}

== Overview ==
Your wiki content here...

{{ThemeEnd}}
</pre>
